Orego

Packages 
Package Description
orego.book
Classes dealing with the opening book, which is generated automatically from a large collection of games by strong human players.
orego.core
Classes dealing with the board, colors, coordinates, etc.
orego.decision  
orego.experiment
Classes for running and analyzing experiments.
orego.heuristic  
orego.mcts
Player classes implementing Monte-Carlo tree search.
orego.patternanalyze  
orego.patterns
Classes dealing with pattern recognition, as described in Gelly et al, "Modification of UCT with Patterns in Monte-Carlo Go".
orego.play
Interface and classes from which players descend.
orego.ui
Contains the main class Orego, which interacts with GTP or the command line.
orego.util
Utility classes for, e.g., representing sets.
orego.wls
